about.summary: A Python client to remotely access the R statistic package via network

name: pyrserve
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "pyRserve" %}
{% set version = "0.9.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 55af2db8f39b5d15550961b3e5b7e5ddfbd07e93796a5cce2a03440bda794d98

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - numpy
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - numpy
    - pytest
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pyRserve

about:
  home: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyRserve/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: 
  summary: A Python client to remotely access the R statistic package via network
  doc_url: 
  dev_url: 

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - trachtok
